    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and treated with so much love. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for its next big adventure, you\u2019ve definitely found it. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
