    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing a level of mechanical preservation rarely seen. The high-revving S54 inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS overhaul already completed. The subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry is optimized with corner-balanced Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, providing exceptional damping and transient response. This example is free of any subframe cracks or VANOS rattle, representing the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated M-division era in showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
