      "description": "This vehicle represents the definitive standard of automotive preservation. Presented in immaculate condition, every facet of this specimen\u2014from its flawless exterior luster to the pristine, showroom-quality interior\u2014testifies to a history of rigorous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically uncompromising and aesthetically peerless, this vehicle offers a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite discerning collectors to acquire this exceptional example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 47500.0,
