    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited to show you this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been totally babied, kept in the garage, and is basically spotless inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
