    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine, collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with a fully serviced VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, preserving the car's celebrated 50:50 weight distribution and torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock, ensuring peak mechanical grip. Finished in factory-spec paint with a showroom-clean underbody, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of analog performance and engineering integrity.",
